{"id":15504,"date":"2025-11-12T08:49:39","date_gmt":"2025-11-12T08:49:39","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/sampreciousmetals.com\/?p=15504"},"modified":"2026-01-13T08:52:06","modified_gmt":"2026-01-13T08:52:06","slug":"sam-precious-metals-academy","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/sampreciousmetals.com\/sam-precious-metals-academy\/","title":{"rendered":"Strengthening Global Academic Pathways for Francophone Communities"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-post\" data-elementor-id=\"15504\" class=\"elementor elementor-15504\" data-elementor-post-type=\"post\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-47a468e elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-eae-slider=\"43894\" data-id=\"47a468e\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-f00c839\" data-eae-slider=\"51650\" data-id=\"f00c839\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1b2e6f5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1b2e6f5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<style>\/*! elementor - v3.22.0 - 24-06-2024 *\/\n.elementor-widget-text-editor.elementor-drop-cap-view-stacked .elementor-drop-cap{background-color:#69727d;color:#fff}.elementor-widget-text-editor.elementor-drop-cap-view-framed .elementor-drop-cap{color:#69727d;border:3px solid;background-color:transparent}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap{margin-top:8px}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap-letter{width:1em;height:1em}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap{float:left;text-align:center;line-height:1;font-size:50px}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap-letter{display:inline-block}<\/style>\t\t\t\t<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Sam Precious Metals is pleased to announce a significant milestone in the advancement of international education within the precious metals sector.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Earlier this year in Paris, <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/sampreciousmetals.com\/message-from-the-chairman\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><b><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Mr. Sami Abu Ahmad<\/span><\/b><\/a><span data-contrast=\"auto\"> formalized an academic cooperation agreement at the <\/span><b><span data-contrast=\"auto\">National Assembly of France<\/span><\/b><span data-contrast=\"auto\"> alongside <\/span><b><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Mr. Herv\u00e9 Diaz<\/span><\/b><span data-contrast=\"auto\"> and <\/span><b><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Mr. Bruno Fuchs<\/span><\/b><span data-contrast=\"auto\">, President and Honorary President of the Circle of French-speaking Students of France.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">This cooperation marks a strategic step toward supporting <\/span><b><span data-contrast=\"auto\">\u00e9tudiants francophones<\/span><\/b><span data-contrast=\"auto\"> not only in France and UAE, but across Europe, Africa, and the Middle East \u2013 regions that hold historic importance in the global gold industry and account for French-speaking nations that include many of the world\u2019s most prominent gold-producing markets.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Through this partnership, French-speaking students will gain structured access to specialized academic and industry pathways, including training in responsible sourcing, compliance, refining sciences, market integrity, and sector-specific governance.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">This initiative aligns closely with the evolution of the <\/span><b><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Sam Training Center<\/span><\/b><span data-contrast=\"auto\">, now known as <\/span><b><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Sam Precious Metals Academy<\/span><\/b><span data-contrast=\"auto\">, which is transitioning into a broader academic body dedicated to elevating educational standards globally. As part of this development, new academic bridges are being established to further serve diverse international communities, including French-speaking markets critical to precious metals supply chains and economic growth.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">By extending these academic foundations to the Francophone world, Sam reaffirms its commitment to education as a tool for structural empowerment, ethical industry development, and long-term international cooperation. This agreement represents not only the strengthening of cultural and academic ties, but also the advancement of communities deeply connected to the global gold economy.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Further academic and enrolment updates will be announced in due course.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-c491f94 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-eae-slider=\"30407\" data-id=\"c491f94\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-7e03156\" data-eae-slider=\"65003\" data-id=\"7e03156\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-70ebe96 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"70ebe96\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<style>\/*! elementor - v3.22.0 - 24-06-2024 *\/\n.elementor-heading-title{padding:0;margin:0;line-height:1}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title[class*=elementor-size-]>a{color:inherit;font-size:inherit;line-height:inherit}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-small{font-size:15px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-medium{font-size:19px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-large{font-size:29px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-xl{font-size:39px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-xxl{font-size:59px}<\/style><h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Renforcer les parcours acad\u00e9miques mondiaux pour les communaut\u00e9s francophones <\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-7c7002e elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-eae-slider=\"48648\" data-id=\"7c7002e\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-c402bf9\" data-eae-slider=\"76941\" data-id=\"c402bf9\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3f91e1d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3f91e1d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Sam Precious Metals a le plaisir d\u2019annoncer une \u00e9tape majeure dans le d\u00e9veloppement de l\u2019\u00e9ducation internationale au sein du secteur des m\u00e9taux pr\u00e9cieux.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:true,&quot;134233118&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:240}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Plus t\u00f4t cette ann\u00e9e, \u00e0 Paris, M.\u202f<\/span><b><span data-contrast=\"none\">Sami Abu Ahmad<\/span><\/b><span data-contrast=\"none\">\u202fa officialis\u00e9 un accord de coop\u00e9ration acad\u00e9mique \u00e0 l\u2019Assembl\u00e9e nationale de France aux c\u00f4t\u00e9s de\u202f<\/span><b><span data-contrast=\"none\">M. Herv\u00e9 Diaz<\/span><\/b><span data-contrast=\"none\">\u202fet\u202f<\/span><b><span data-contrast=\"none\">M. Bruno Fuchs<\/span><\/b><span data-contrast=\"none\">, respectivement Pr\u00e9sident et Pr\u00e9sident d\u2019honneur du\u202f<\/span><b><span data-contrast=\"none\">Cercle des \u00c9tudiants Francophones de France<\/span><\/b><span data-contrast=\"none\">.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:true,&quot;134233118&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:240}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Cette coop\u00e9ration marque une avanc\u00e9e strat\u00e9gique pour soutenir les\u202f<\/span><b><span data-contrast=\"none\">\u00e9tudiants francophones<\/span><\/b><span data-contrast=\"none\">, non seulement en France et aux \u00c9mirats arabes unis, mais \u00e9galement \u00e0 travers l\u2019Europe, l\u2019Afrique et le Moyen-Orient \u2014 des r\u00e9gions qui occupent une place historique dans l\u2019industrie mondiale de l\u2019or et regroupent de nombreuses nations francophones parmi les plus grands march\u00e9s aurif\u00e8res du monde.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:true,&quot;134233118&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:240}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Gr\u00e2ce \u00e0 ce partenariat, les \u00e9tudiants francophones b\u00e9n\u00e9ficieront d\u2019un\u202f<\/span><b><span data-contrast=\"none\">acc\u00e8s structur\u00e9 \u00e0 des parcours acad\u00e9miques et professionnels sp\u00e9cialis\u00e9s<\/span><\/b><span data-contrast=\"none\">, incluant des formations en\u202f<\/span><b><span data-contrast=\"none\">approvisionnement responsable<\/span><\/b><span data-contrast=\"none\">,\u202f<\/span><b><span data-contrast=\"none\">conformit\u00e9<\/span><\/b><span data-contrast=\"none\">,\u202f<\/span><b><span data-contrast=\"none\">sciences du raffinage<\/span><\/b><span data-contrast=\"none\">,\u202f<\/span><b><span data-contrast=\"none\">int\u00e9grit\u00e9 du march\u00e9<\/span><\/b><span data-contrast=\"none\">\u202fet\u202f<\/span><b><span data-contrast=\"none\">gouvernance sectorielle<\/span><\/b><span data-contrast=\"none\">.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:true,&quot;134233118&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:240}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Cette initiative s\u2019inscrit dans la continuit\u00e9 de l\u2019\u00e9volution du\u202f<\/span><b><span data-contrast=\"none\">Centre de Formation Sam<\/span><\/b><span data-contrast=\"none\">, d\u00e9sormais connu sous le nom de <\/span><b><span data-contrast=\"none\">Sam Precious Metals Academy<\/span><\/b><span data-contrast=\"none\">, qui se transforme en un organisme acad\u00e9mique plus vaste, d\u00e9di\u00e9 \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9l\u00e9vation des standards \u00e9ducatifs \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9chelle mondiale. Dans ce cadre, de\u202f<\/span><b><span data-contrast=\"none\">nouveaux ponts acad\u00e9miques<\/span><\/b><span data-contrast=\"none\">\u202fsont \u00e9tablis pour mieux servir les communaut\u00e9s internationales, notamment les march\u00e9s francophones essentiels aux cha\u00eenes d\u2019approvisionnement et \u00e0 la croissance \u00e9conomique des m\u00e9taux pr\u00e9cieux.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:true,&quot;134233118&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:240}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span data-contrast=\"none\">En \u00e9tendant ces fondations acad\u00e9miques au monde francophone, Sam r\u00e9affirme son\u202f<\/span><b><span data-contrast=\"none\">engagement envers l\u2019\u00e9ducation<\/span><\/b><span data-contrast=\"none\">comme outil d\u2019<\/span><b><span data-contrast=\"none\">autonomisation structurelle<\/span><\/b><span data-contrast=\"none\">, de\u202f<\/span><b><span data-contrast=\"none\">d\u00e9veloppement \u00e9thique<\/span><\/b><span data-contrast=\"none\">\u202fdu secteur et de\u202f<\/span><b><span data-contrast=\"none\">coop\u00e9ration internationale durable<\/span><\/b><span data-contrast=\"none\">. Cet accord repr\u00e9sente non seulement un renforcement des liens culturels et acad\u00e9miques, mais aussi un progr\u00e8s concret pour les communaut\u00e9s profond\u00e9ment connect\u00e9es \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9conomie mondiale de l\u2019or.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:true,&quot;134233118&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:240}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Des mises \u00e0 jour suppl\u00e9mentaires concernant les programmes acad\u00e9miques et les inscriptions seront annonc\u00e9es prochainement.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:true,&quot;134233118&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:240}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-0cc16af elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-eae-slider=\"86590\" data-id=\"0cc16af\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-33d2360\" data-eae-slider=\"28474\" data-id=\"33d2360\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2b58328 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"2b58328\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">\u062a\u0639\u0632\u064a\u0632 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0633\u0627\u0631\u0627\u062a \u0627\u0644\u0623\u0643\u0627\u062f\u064a\u0645\u064a\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0627\u0644\u0645\u064a\u0629 \u0644\u0644\u0645\u062c\u062a\u0645\u0639\u0627\u062a \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0627\u0637\u0642\u0629 \u0628\u0627\u0644\u0641\u0631\u0646\u0633\u064a\u0629 <\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-b14fd2d elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-eae-slider=\"19311\" data-id=\"b14fd2d\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-